# Extension Command Provider Service Registration
#
# This file is used by Java's ServiceLoader to discover extension command providers.
# Extensions should create their own META-INF/services/org.qubership.itool.cli.ExtensionCommandProvider
# file and add their provider class names to it.
#
# Example:
# org.qubership.itool.extension.MyExtensionCommandProvider
#
# No core providers are registered here - this file serves as documentation
# for the extension mechanism.
